headline: 2 Reasons to Like ZTS (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: Over the last six months, Zoetis’s shares have sunk to $129.91, producing a disappointing 16.4% loss - a stark contrast to the S&P 500’s 7.2% gain. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
